      %h1 ABOUT GAANA PEHCHAANA
      .line
      .full-box
        %h2 Missions
        %p Gaana Pehchaana - A New Way to Enjoy Hindi Film Music is a not-for-profit organization dedicated to promotion and appreciation of Hindi Film Music from India.  It is a unique and fun way of promoting Hindi Film Music through a game show format, live performances, on-line games, blogs and discussion forums.
        %h2 Hindi Film Music - A National Treasure
        %p Hindi films have delighted audiences and listeners with their music from as far back as the 1930's all the way to the 2010's and are truly a national treasure! The music from the films has consistently set a higher standard of excellence and entertainment than the films themselves, and often outlasts them in popularity by decades. Yet, the people behind these songs - composers, singers, lyricists and instrumentalists – don't get anywhere near the recognition that the stars acting in the films do.  Gaana Pehchaana is a small effort to pay tribute to all these artists and their creations which have enriched the lives of millions of people over many decades.
        %h2 Gaana Pehchaana Features
        %p The primary vehicle for Gaana Pehchaana’s tribute to Hindi Film Music is a live event that features fun and competitive game formats involving clips from the songs.  These events pay tribute to the geniuses that created these gems of music and lyrics, highlight interesting facts about the process of creating these masterpieces, and often include live performances.  A typical event features clips from nearly 100 songs, often accompanied in a sing-along by the audience!  The audience often goes home humming their favorite songs and, we hope, appreciative of the enjoyment and enrichment that Hindi Film Music has brought to all our lives!
        %p Gaana Pehchaana also features a blog with articles reminding readers of the creative gems from Hindi Film Music, old and new.  Future plans include on-line games, critical reviews of new albums and recommendations on songs to listen to and add to listeners’ collections.
        %p While a long way from actually raising any funds, any such funds raised from the efforts of Gaana Pehchaana will be entirely donated to causes benefiting the artists who created Hindi Film Music over the ages, and to programs that foster the continued appreciation of these national treasures.  
        %p Gaana Pehchaana is also available to anchor fund-raising events for other non-profit organizations.
