        %p During a typical live event, called GP Night, different game formats are used to highlight Hindi Film Music and organize fun games that can be played by whole audiences or a few teams.  Click on the video link below to see a quick intro into the GP Night format and live footage.
        %p Here are some more details on the formats used in recent GP events.
