        %h2 Teek Taak Ho
        %p This game introduces the Gaana Pehchaana game concept and warms up the audience.  It uses the familiar Tic-Tac-Toe format shown below. The audience is divided into two teams, the X's and the O's.  Clicking on the music note in each square plays a song clip.  Correctly recognizing the clip places the team's symbol in that square.   The objective of this game is the same is that of a Tic-Tac-Toe game - a straight line connecting three of the teams symbols.
