        %h2 Raaga Malika
        %p The picture below shows the ''game board'' for Raaga Malika.  Music clips are organized into themes such as ''Dil Se'' (songs with Dil in the answer),  or ''Ek Musafir Ek Hasina'' (songs with Ek in the answer).  Clicking on each musical note plays a song clip from that theme. Answers are selected by the audience from a multiple choice list using a keypad given to each team.  The clips get more difficult and the points are higher as we go up the musical scale from Sa to Pa.  The faster the answer, the more the points.  Wrong answers get negative points.  The team with the most points after all songs are cleared is declared the winner.
